dct_description_sm: Drawn by E. C. and C. Y. Dean ; Joseph J. Stephens. Government photo-litho-zincographer ; Photo-lithographed at the Surveyor General's Office, Perth, W.A.
Bar scale of miles and chains.
Shows railroads, roads, villages and towns, various place names (peaks, waterways, plains), various locations (goldfields, stations, wells, etc.).
Dates, names, and routes of several explorers and surveyors.
